  "description": "<p>Overstuffed with 800 fill-power hydrophobic down, the Riff is 3-season side-sleeping perfection. Equipped with Nemo\u2019s award winning Thermo Gills\u2122 allow you to dial-in the perfect temperature for those times where your bag is a bit too warm, but the air outside is a bit too cold to unzip, think of them like cracking a widow.</p><ul><li>Shell is constructed from ripstop OSMO\u2122 fabric with soft nylon taffeta lining, both treated with a DWR finish</li><li>Zippered Thermo Gill\u2122 vents let you release extra body heat without letting cold air in</li><li>800 fill-power RDS certified hydrophobic down wont wet-out, staying lofty and warm in all conditions</li><li>Spoon\u2122 shaped athletic cut is designed for side sleepers</li><li>Vertical baffles that channel warmth along your body, reducing cold sports</li><li>Insulated hood with pillow pocket keeps your noggin warm on cold nights</li><li>Blanket Fold\u2122 external draft collar and full-length internal draft collar helps seal in the heat</li><li>Water resistant breathable footbox has a DWR finish to protect it and you from moist tent walls</li><li>Left-sided zippers on men\u2019s and right-sided zippers on women\u2019s allow Riff\u2122 to zip together into a double bag</li><li>YKK zippers with Nemo\u2019s zipper plow, means no more snags</li><li>Includes a compression sack and mesh home storage sack</li></ul>",
